{"id":175,"parent_id":158,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":175,"title":"Deuteronomy 17","subtitle":"","short_title":"Deut.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 17"],[".studySummary",["i","Those who worship false gods will be put to death—Priests and judges are to determine the hard cases—Kings are not to acquire horses, wives, or gold for themselves—The king must study the laws of God daily."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.1","order":"02.06.017.15823"},["b","1"],"Thou shalt not sacrifice unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God",["i","any"],"bullock, or sheep, wherein is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"blemish"],",",["i","or"],"any",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"evilfavouredness"],": for that",["i","is"],"an abomination unto the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.2","order":"02.06.017.15824"},["b","2"],"¶If there be found among you, within any of thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"gates"],"which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, man or woman, that hath wrought wickedness in the sight of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, in",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"transgressing"],"his covenant,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.3","order":"02.06.017.15825"},["b","3"],"And hath gone and served other gods, and worshipped them, either the sun, or moon, or any of the host of heaven, which I have not commanded;"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.4","order":"02.06.017.15826"},["b","4"],"And it be told thee, and thou hast heard",["i","of it,"],"and inquired diligently, and, behold,",["i","it be"],"true,",["i","and"],"the thing certain,",["i","that"],"such abomination is wrought in Israel:"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.5","order":"02.06.017.15827"},["b","5"],"Then shalt thou bring forth that man or that woman, which have committed that wicked thing, unto thy gates,",["i","even"],"that man or that woman, and shalt",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"stone"],"them with stones, till they",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"die"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.6","order":"02.06.017.15828"},["b","6"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"At the mouth"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"two"],"witnesses, or three witnesses, shall he that is worthy of death be put to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"death"],";",["i","but"],"at the mouth of one witness he shall not be put to death."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.7","order":"02.06.017.15829"},["b","7"],"The hands of the witnesses shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"first"],"upon him to put him to death, and afterward the hands of all the people. So thou shalt put the evil away from among you."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.8","order":"02.06.017.15830"},["b","8"],"¶If there arise a matter too hard for thee in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"judgment"],",",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"between"],"blood and blood, between plea and plea, and between stroke and stroke,",["i","being"],"matters of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"controversy"],"within thy gates: then shalt thou arise, and get thee up into the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_8d"},"place"],"which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God shall choose;"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.9","order":"02.06.017.15831"},["b","9"],"And thou shalt come unto the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"priests"],"the Levites, and unto the judge that shall be in those days, and inquire; and they shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"shew thee"],"the sentence of judgment:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.10","order":"02.06.017.15832"},["b","10"],"And thou shalt do according to the sentence, which they of that place which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"shall choose shall shew thee; and thou shalt observe to do according to all that they inform thee:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.11","order":"02.06.017.15833"},["b","11"],"According to the sentence of the law which they shall teach thee, and according to the judgment which they shall tell thee, thou shalt do: thou shalt not decline from the sentence which they shall shew thee,",["i","to"],"the right hand, nor",["i","to"],"the left."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.12","order":"02.06.017.15834"},["b","12"],"And the man that will do presumptuously, and will not hearken unto the priest that standeth to minister there before the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God, or unto the judge, even that man shall die: and thou shalt put away the evil from Israel."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.13","order":"02.06.017.15835"},["b","13"],"And all the people shall hear, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"fear"],", and do no more presumptuously."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.14","order":"02.06.017.15836"},["b","14"],"¶When thou art come unto the land which the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God giveth thee, and shalt possess it, and shalt dwell therein, and shalt say, I will set a king over me, like as all the nations that",["i","are"],"about me;"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.15","order":"02.06.017.15837"},["b","15"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Thou"],"shalt in any wise set",["i","him"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"king"],"over thee, whom the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"thy God shall choose:",["i","one"],"from among thy brethren shalt thou set king over thee: thou mayest not set a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"stranger"],"over thee, which",["i","is"],"not thy brother."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.16","order":"02.06.017.15838"},["b","16"],"But he shall not multiply",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"horses"],"to himself, nor cause the people to return to Egypt, to the end that he should multiply horses: forasmuch as the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath said unto you, Ye shall henceforth",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"return"],"no more that way."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.17","order":"02.06.017.15839"},["b","17"],"Neither shall he multiply",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"wives"],"to himself, that his heart turn not away: neither shall he greatly",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"multiply"],"to himself silver and gold."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.18","order":"02.06.017.15840"},["b","18"],"And it shall be, when he sitteth upon the throne of his kingdom, that he shall write him a copy of this law in a book out of",["i","that which is"],"before the priests the Levites:"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.19","order":"02.06.017.15841"},["b","19"],"And it shall be with him, and he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"read"],"therein all the days of his life: that he may learn to fear the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"his God, to keep all the words of this law and these statutes, to do them:"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.20","order":"02.06.017.15842"},["b","20"],"That his heart be not lifted up above his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"brethren"],", and that he",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"turn"],"not aside from the commandment,",["i","to"],"the right hand, or",["i","to"],"the left: to the end that he may prolong",["i","his"],"days in his kingdom, he, and his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"children"],", in the midst of Israel."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.1a","order":"02.06.017.15843"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/22.20"},"Lev. 22:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.1b","order":"02.06.017.15845"},["b","1b"],["span.small","HEB"],"defect."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.2a","order":"02.06.017.15847"},["b","2a"],["span.small","IE"],"cities, towns (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.8"},"v. 8"],")."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.2b","order":"02.06.017.15849"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/23.16"},"Josh. 23:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.5a","order":"02.06.017.15851"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.4"},"Lev. 20:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.5b","order":"02.06.017.15853"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/capital-punishment"},"TG Capital Punishment"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.6a","order":"02.06.017.15855"},["b","6a"],["span.small","IE"],"On the evidence."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.6b","order":"02.06.017.15857"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness"},"TG Witness"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.6c","order":"02.06.017.15859"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/capital-punishment"},"TG Capital Punishment"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.7a","order":"02.06.017.15861"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/13.9"},"Deut. 13:9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.7.3-11"},"John 8:7 (3–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.8a","order":"02.06.017.15863"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/29.28.28-29"},"Mosiah 29:28 (28–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.8b","order":"02.06.017.15865"},["b","8b"],["span.small","IE"],"regarding degrees of manslaughter, etc."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.8c","order":"02.06.017.15867"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/44.24"},"Ezek. 44:24"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/disputations"},"TG Disputations"],"."],["div",{"id":"8d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/deut/17.8d","order":"02.06.017.15869"},["b","8d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptu